WEBVTT

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:06.280
Go pack your bag.

00:00:06.320 --> 00:00:08.400
Where are you sending me?

00:00:08.440 --> 00:00:11.440
Win and that woman
aren't anything special, right?

00:00:11.440 --> 00:00:14.440
I've been so hurt by love
I don't dare open my heart again.

00:00:14.480 --> 00:00:17.960
But maybe she's the one
who'll make you take that risk again.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:20.120
Khun Win, I can take it myself.

00:00:20.120 --> 00:00:21.680
But I'm happy to help.

00:00:21.720 --> 00:00:22.760
Are you flirting with me?

00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:25.000
We've come this far.
No need to flirt anymore, right?

00:00:25.040 --> 00:00:27.200
So Wanneung got the role
in this movie, right?

00:00:28.240 --> 00:00:30.440
And do you know what
made me happiest?

00:00:30.480 --> 00:00:34.160
In my dream, you were in it too.

00:01:39.640 --> 00:01:41.040
Why...

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:43.440
You're up so early, Khun Win.

00:01:48.120 --> 00:01:50.360
I'm still sleepy.

00:01:59.320 --> 00:02:00.920
Khun Win.

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:02.200
Don't stop.

00:02:02.240 --> 00:02:04.600
It's still early.

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:09.360
It's already morning.

00:02:12.840 --> 00:02:14.320
Khun Win.

00:02:14.440 --> 00:02:16.320
Don't...

00:02:18.920 --> 00:02:20.400
Wanneung.

00:02:21.160 --> 00:02:23.040
Khun Win.

00:02:23.240 --> 00:02:24.880
Don't.

00:02:25.320 --> 00:02:26.560
How about...

00:02:26.840 --> 00:02:30.120
How about we do something
that'll make us sweat a little?

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:31.160
Why?

00:02:31.160 --> 00:02:32.960
What are you talking about?

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:34.680
I think I'll go shower.

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:35.760
You…

00:02:35.760 --> 00:02:37.000
You're not going.

00:02:37.360 --> 00:02:40.040
-I'm going to shower.
-No, no, you're not going.

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:43.080
Let go of me. I can't anymore.

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:45.560
What do you mean you can't?
I still can.

00:02:45.840 --> 00:02:47.600
What are you talking about?

00:02:47.680 --> 00:02:50.000
Don't be naughty.

00:02:50.040 --> 00:02:51.680
-Naughty?
-That's enough.

00:02:52.280 --> 00:02:53.960
What do you think I'm gonna do?

00:02:56.280 --> 00:02:57.520
Well...

00:02:58.760 --> 00:03:01.000
You think I'm going to do
what we did last night?

00:03:02.440 --> 00:03:03.720
Then...

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:05.160
Isn't that it?

00:04:30.920 --> 00:04:32.120
This sucks.

00:04:32.160 --> 00:04:34.320
I got woken up just to exercise.

00:04:34.640 --> 00:04:36.680
-I was sleeping so well.
-What were you saying?

00:04:38.280 --> 00:04:39.640
Nothing.

00:04:39.680 --> 00:04:43.080
Nothing at all.
Not a thing.

00:04:43.120 --> 00:04:45.360
I wasn't complaining.

00:04:45.400 --> 00:04:47.880
Waking up early to exercise like this...

00:04:47.920 --> 00:04:50.480
That feels so refreshing.

00:04:50.520 --> 00:04:53.080
After yoga, we're going for a run
next, right?

00:04:53.120 --> 00:04:55.320
Sounds great.

00:05:03.280 --> 00:05:04.640
Or...

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:06.440
do you want to do
what we did last night?

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:10.000
What we did last night

00:05:10.040 --> 00:05:12.200
counts as exercise too.

00:05:13.000 --> 00:05:14.880
Khun Win.

00:05:29.320 --> 00:05:30.360
Wanneung.

00:05:30.800 --> 00:05:33.760
You don't want to run
or do yoga, right?

00:05:34.720 --> 00:05:35.800
That's right.

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:38.000
So we don't have to run today,
right?

00:05:38.760 --> 00:05:40.600
Then let's go find something to eat.

00:05:41.280 --> 00:05:42.520
Wait.

00:05:43.560 --> 00:05:46.320
We're not running
and we're not doing yoga.

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:49.400
But we're going swimming.

00:05:53.160 --> 00:05:54.720
Swimming?

00:05:55.640 --> 00:05:57.320
You know I'm afraid of water.

00:05:57.360 --> 00:05:58.360
No.

00:05:58.400 --> 00:06:00.240
Just try it first. Come on.

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:01.520
No, Khun Win.

00:06:01.560 --> 00:06:03.520
No, Khun Win. No.

00:06:03.560 --> 00:06:05.080
Don't hold yourself back.

00:06:05.200 --> 00:06:07.280
-Khun Win, please.
-Come on.

00:06:11.920 --> 00:06:13.040
How is it?

00:06:13.880 --> 00:06:15.200
Are you still scared?

00:06:18.240 --> 00:06:19.400
Yeah.

00:06:19.960 --> 00:06:20.960
Okay.

00:06:22.080 --> 00:06:23.960
Hold my hand and take a deep breath.

00:06:39.320 --> 00:06:40.640
Feeling better?

00:06:40.680 --> 00:06:41.680
No.

00:06:44.080 --> 00:06:45.360
-Khun Win.
-Wanneung.

00:06:45.400 --> 00:06:46.400
Khun Win.

00:06:48.640 --> 00:06:49.840
Khun Win.

00:06:50.560 --> 00:06:51.560
Khun Win.

00:06:51.800 --> 00:06:52.800
Khun Win.

00:06:53.920 --> 00:06:55.000
Khun Win.

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:00.400
See? There's nothing to it.

00:07:11.760 --> 00:07:13.000
Do you want to come down?

00:07:15.160 --> 00:07:16.480
No.

00:07:17.600 --> 00:07:19.840
I'm right here, remember?

00:07:22.600 --> 00:07:24.280
Try touching the water first.

00:07:41.400 --> 00:07:42.400
Khun Win.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:43.920
-Khun Win.
-Wanneung.

00:07:43.960 --> 00:07:45.600
-Watch out.
-Khun Win!

00:08:42.880 --> 00:08:44.080
Wanneung.

00:08:45.800 --> 00:08:46.880
Stand straight.

00:08:46.920 --> 00:08:48.080
Wanneung.

00:08:49.160 --> 00:08:50.920
Hey, Khun Win.

00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:53.920
I don't want to swim.

00:08:55.160 --> 00:08:56.280
Easy.

00:08:57.360 --> 00:08:58.640
I'm right here.

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:02.600
Right here.

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:07.480
See? It's nothing.

00:09:09.960 --> 00:09:11.360
Take a deep breath.

00:09:20.240 --> 00:09:21.640
Slowly put your foot down.

00:09:29.240 --> 00:09:30.640
Do you trust me?

00:09:42.720 --> 00:09:44.120
Look at me.

00:09:45.200 --> 00:09:46.280
Now try smiling.

00:09:49.640 --> 00:09:51.240
See? You can smile.

00:09:55.560 --> 00:09:56.680
See? It's nothing.

00:09:56.680 --> 00:09:57.800
Don't.

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:01.000
Wanneung.

00:10:01.400 --> 00:10:03.160
You started teasing me.

00:10:03.920 --> 00:10:05.200
Khun Win.

00:10:05.200 --> 00:10:06.560
Okay, I'm letting go.

00:10:06.600 --> 00:10:08.560
-Here I go.
-Khun Win!

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:10.240
Let go of me.

00:10:10.920 --> 00:10:12.040
See? You're standing.

00:10:16.440 --> 00:10:18.160
Don't leave me.

00:10:55.640 --> 00:10:57.320
(Mom)

00:11:05.480 --> 00:11:09.200
(Mom)

00:11:10.600 --> 00:11:12.080
Hello, Mom.

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:14.320
I saw your news on Facebook.

00:11:14.320 --> 00:11:16.120
Did you become an actress?

00:11:16.160 --> 00:11:17.680
Why didn't you tell us?

00:11:17.680 --> 00:11:20.640
You never even called to tell Mom and Dad.

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:24.320
I wanted to succeed first.

00:11:24.360 --> 00:11:26.880
So Dad and you would know I could do it.

00:11:27.120 --> 00:11:30.000
Do you know your dad was so excited?

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:33.000
He told all the customers at the shop.

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:35.080
Really, Mom?

00:11:36.640 --> 00:11:38.520
You're amazing.

00:11:38.560 --> 00:11:41.640
Your dad and I are very proud of you.

00:11:41.800 --> 00:11:43.680
Thank you, Mom.

00:11:43.960 --> 00:11:46.000
I love you and Dad.

00:12:21.400 --> 00:12:23.480
Why are you smiling from so far away?

00:12:23.840 --> 00:12:24.920
Well...

00:12:24.960 --> 00:12:28.120
My mom just called and said...

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:30.840
they’re very proud of me.

00:12:30.840 --> 00:12:32.960
I wanted to tell you...

00:12:32.960 --> 00:12:35.480
thank you, Win.

00:12:36.280 --> 00:12:37.720
What are you thanking me for?

00:12:38.640 --> 00:12:41.840
For always pushing me forward

00:12:41.880 --> 00:12:45.480
and encouraging me every day.

00:12:46.320 --> 00:12:48.360
If it weren't for you...

00:12:52.280 --> 00:12:54.080
and P’Waanwaan,

00:12:54.080 --> 00:12:55.880
if it weren't for both of you,

00:12:55.920 --> 00:12:58.000
I probably wouldn't have gotten the film.

00:13:01.960 --> 00:13:03.320
Right, this is the script.

00:13:03.360 --> 00:13:04.560
Take this and memorize it.

00:13:04.560 --> 00:13:07.040
Then act it out for me.

00:13:11.720 --> 00:13:13.840
All of this?

00:13:13.880 --> 00:13:16.480
Just do the parts I marked.

00:13:16.520 --> 00:13:20.200
Even the marked parts are a lot.
All of it?

00:13:20.200 --> 00:13:22.160
Or just the first page?

00:13:22.200 --> 00:13:23.720
If you can't even do this,

00:13:23.760 --> 00:13:25.640
then stop thinking
about becoming an actress.

00:13:29.960 --> 00:13:30.960
Hey.

00:13:31.000 --> 00:13:32.400
Did you forget?

00:13:32.440 --> 00:13:35.200
I'm just your fake wife.

00:13:35.200 --> 00:13:36.920
I don't understand

00:13:36.960 --> 00:13:39.440
why you're asking
about my background.

00:13:39.640 --> 00:13:42.200
-I'm totally confused.
-You, you.

00:13:42.920 --> 00:13:44.320
Tone it down.

00:13:44.400 --> 00:13:45.880
-Less, less.
-Okay.

00:13:45.880 --> 00:13:47.200
-Keep it softer.
-Okay.

00:13:47.360 --> 00:13:50.720
Not everyone can...

00:13:50.880 --> 00:13:53.200
-say everything...
-No.

00:13:53.240 --> 00:13:55.880
It's not everyone

00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:58.520
who can...

00:14:17.360 --> 00:14:18.640
Wanneung.

00:14:19.600 --> 00:14:21.080
That's enough.

00:14:21.120 --> 00:14:23.360
I can't do it.

00:14:23.680 --> 00:14:25.240
You have to.

00:14:25.280 --> 00:14:27.400
I already vouched for you.

00:14:28.200 --> 00:14:29.560
Vouched for me?

00:14:30.200 --> 00:14:31.760
What do you mean?

00:14:33.600 --> 00:14:35.080
Nothing. Forget it.

00:14:35.680 --> 00:14:37.600
Don't think you can't do it.

00:14:42.440 --> 00:14:43.520
Wanneung.

00:14:44.520 --> 00:14:45.760
Listen to me.

00:14:47.920 --> 00:14:50.560
You have to truly feel every line you say.

00:14:51.320 --> 00:14:53.400
If you don't feel it, don't say it.

00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:56.720
Think of yourself as that character.

00:14:57.320 --> 00:14:59.080
Why would they say that line?

00:14:59.200 --> 00:15:00.800
What are they feeling?

00:15:01.880 --> 00:15:05.520
Don't just think you're
playing that character.

00:15:07.320 --> 00:15:08.720
You understand, right?

00:15:09.720 --> 00:15:11.720
I believe you can do it.

00:15:24.240 --> 00:15:26.120
Not everyone

00:15:28.600 --> 00:15:32.480
can say everything they truly feel.

00:15:37.320 --> 00:15:38.920
You wouldn't understand.

00:15:41.200 --> 00:15:44.520
How hard it is

00:15:45.720 --> 00:15:47.560
to keep your feelings locked inside.

00:15:54.880 --> 00:15:58.040
Wanting to tell someone
you love them...

00:16:00.600 --> 00:16:03.320
but not having the right to say those words.

00:16:06.440 --> 00:16:08.400
Because you think...

00:16:09.880 --> 00:16:11.080
that you...

00:16:11.120 --> 00:16:13.480
don't deserve them.

00:16:13.920 --> 00:16:14.920
You.

00:16:25.600 --> 00:16:26.640
Pass.

00:16:28.240 --> 00:16:29.520
Really?

00:16:32.640 --> 00:16:35.360
Tell me what the character
was thinking just now.

00:16:35.360 --> 00:16:36.440
Well, I...

00:16:43.160 --> 00:16:44.680
thought...

00:16:45.240 --> 00:16:47.360
that they weren't worthy.

00:16:47.720 --> 00:16:49.200
Like...

00:16:49.200 --> 00:16:51.400
they weren't good enough for her.

00:16:51.480 --> 00:16:55.480
And they were afraid that if
they said how they really felt,

00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:59.040
it might ruin the good thing
they had right now.

00:17:00.840 --> 00:17:04.640
So they'd rather stay
in their own sweet dream

00:17:04.640 --> 00:17:06.000
a little longer.

00:17:07.240 --> 00:17:08.600
What's with the "well," Wanneung?

00:17:08.600 --> 00:17:10.800
So what were you
really thinking?

00:17:12.560 --> 00:17:13.640
Well...

00:17:14.240 --> 00:17:15.560
I thought...

00:17:15.600 --> 00:17:17.680
I'm tired.

00:17:17.760 --> 00:17:19.520
Let's stop here for now.

00:17:19.720 --> 00:17:21.160
I can't go on anymore.

00:17:21.800 --> 00:17:23.040
Alright.

00:17:23.120 --> 00:17:24.440
But if...

00:17:24.760 --> 00:17:26.720
you can act like that
every time,

00:17:27.080 --> 00:17:28.720
you'll be able to play
any role.

00:17:30.000 --> 00:17:31.600
Thank you, Khun Win.

00:17:32.200 --> 00:17:34.120
Hearing you say that

00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:36.800
really gives me a lot of motivation.

00:17:37.640 --> 00:17:39.040
Very good.

00:17:39.080 --> 00:17:40.320
Thank you.

00:18:05.680 --> 00:18:07.680
Not everyone

00:18:07.720 --> 00:18:11.480
can say everything
they truly feel.

00:18:27.640 --> 00:18:28.720
Hello, Tom.

00:18:28.760 --> 00:18:29.840
What's up, Win?

00:18:31.080 --> 00:18:32.800
I want to know

00:18:32.800 --> 00:18:34.760
how we can be sure

00:18:34.840 --> 00:18:37.200
when we love someone

00:18:37.240 --> 00:18:39.720
enough to risk starting over again.

00:18:40.320 --> 00:18:41.640
Who are you talking about?

00:18:42.600 --> 00:18:43.720
Wanneung?

00:18:44.360 --> 00:18:45.680
Just answer first.

00:18:45.720 --> 00:18:48.600
When I'm sure,

00:18:48.960 --> 00:18:50.760
I'll tell you everything.

00:18:51.760 --> 00:18:54.000
If one day you're still scared

00:18:54.200 --> 00:18:55.600
even though you know it's risky,

00:18:55.720 --> 00:18:57.200
but you still want to try,

00:18:57.960 --> 00:18:59.000
that's the moment

00:18:59.520 --> 00:19:01.280
you've fallen in love
with that person.

00:19:06.560 --> 00:19:07.680
Okay.

00:19:07.800 --> 00:19:09.200
Thanks a lot, Tom.

00:20:10.560 --> 00:20:11.840
Khun Win.

00:20:11.960 --> 00:20:13.360
What are you doing?

00:20:15.400 --> 00:20:17.440
I saw you sleeping,

00:20:17.520 --> 00:20:19.440
so I was going to cover you
with this blanket.

00:20:43.560 --> 00:20:45.000
Thank you.

00:21:10.400 --> 00:21:12.480
Dress up nicely
and meet me at the restaurant.

00:21:13.560 --> 00:21:15.480
Excuse me
I’m in a hurry

00:21:15.480 --> 00:21:16.680
Don’t think

00:21:16.680 --> 00:21:19.040
that Win would be serious
about someone like you

00:22:02.660 --> 00:22:04.500
Oh, you're leaving already?

00:22:04.780 --> 00:22:06.980
Of course. You're the doctor
in charge of the patient.

00:22:06.980 --> 00:22:08.140
You told me to go home,
so I'm going home.

00:22:08.140 --> 00:22:09.540
And you still ask?

00:22:09.660 --> 00:22:11.380
It's because of that mouth of yours.

00:22:11.420 --> 00:22:12.620
That's why you're still single.

00:22:12.660 --> 00:22:13.900
Hey.

00:22:14.540 --> 00:22:16.020
So how are you getting home?

00:22:16.100 --> 00:22:18.020
Your car is completely wrecked,
isn't it?

00:22:19.100 --> 00:22:20.420
None of your business.

00:22:33.060 --> 00:22:34.940
Not even a single taxi.

00:22:42.900 --> 00:22:43.940
Hey.

00:22:44.220 --> 00:22:45.860
Get in. I'll take you home.

00:23:04.660 --> 00:23:06.260
Just take it as my apology.

00:23:06.460 --> 00:23:08.020
For what I said earlier.

00:23:10.460 --> 00:23:11.980
Good that you know.

00:23:28.620 --> 00:23:30.380
Since you're giving me a ride anyway,

00:23:30.460 --> 00:23:31.700
let's stop to grab some food.

00:23:31.820 --> 00:23:33.700
I'm so sick of hospital food.

00:23:33.740 --> 00:23:35.420
Sure, but...

00:23:35.420 --> 00:23:36.620
you're paying.

00:23:36.620 --> 00:23:37.860
So stingy.

00:23:38.500 --> 00:23:39.500
Hey.

00:23:39.580 --> 00:23:42.860
One meal won't make
your leg hair fall out.

00:23:42.860 --> 00:23:44.340
Watch your mouth.

00:23:44.380 --> 00:23:46.100
I don't have leg hair.

00:24:15.660 --> 00:24:17.740
Dress up nicely
and meet me at the restaurant.

00:24:17.780 --> 00:24:19.780
I sent you the location on LINE.

00:24:29.300 --> 00:24:30.820
What a fancy place.

00:24:31.180 --> 00:24:33.580
I need to dress up.

00:25:36.380 --> 00:25:37.500
Perfect.

00:26:04.260 --> 00:26:05.980
May I see this ring?

00:26:06.260 --> 00:26:07.420
Of course.

00:26:12.340 --> 00:26:13.340
Thank you.

00:26:22.460 --> 00:26:24.780
Wow, that ring fits you perfectly.

00:27:14.900 --> 00:27:16.180
Khun Win.

00:27:16.260 --> 00:27:17.700
What are you doing?

00:27:19.860 --> 00:27:21.940
I'd like to see another ring...

00:27:26.660 --> 00:27:29.100
around this size, please.

00:27:36.620 --> 00:27:38.700
I'm looking for a ring for a scene.

00:27:38.740 --> 00:27:41.820
The production team asked me
to find one for another actor too.

00:27:41.860 --> 00:27:43.100
For May?

00:27:43.100 --> 00:27:46.580
I heard you're acting
in a movie with May again.

00:27:48.860 --> 00:27:49.980
Yes.

00:27:51.700 --> 00:27:53.100
Please wait a moment.

00:28:08.060 --> 00:28:09.060
You.

00:28:09.500 --> 00:28:10.940
-May
-Look

00:28:10.940 --> 00:28:12.220
May

00:28:12.540 --> 00:28:13.940
-Is that her
-Hey

00:28:14.220 --> 00:28:15.220
Hey

00:28:15.580 --> 00:28:16.580
Hey

00:28:18.020 --> 00:28:19.060
Hey

00:28:19.060 --> 00:28:21.220
Why are you walking so fast
I can’t keep up

00:28:21.260 --> 00:28:22.540
If you can’t keep up
then run

00:28:22.580 --> 00:28:24.380
I don’t feel like taking
photos with fans right now

00:28:24.420 --> 00:28:27.100
Wait, hey
wait for me

00:28:27.140 --> 00:28:28.220
Hey

00:28:48.500 --> 00:28:49.500
Here’s the menu

00:28:49.500 --> 00:28:51.220
We’ll come back shortly
to take your order

00:28:51.260 --> 00:28:52.260
Okay

00:29:49.820 --> 00:29:52.060
Or maybe I dressed up
too much today

00:29:55.020 --> 00:29:56.580
Restroom

00:30:04.860 --> 00:30:05.860
Well...

