00:55:25.653 --> 00:55:28.773
And I won’t have to feel like this anymore.

00:55:53.093 --> 00:55:54.093
Wanneung.

00:55:54.533 --> 00:55:55.533
Wanneung.

00:55:55.853 --> 00:55:56.893
Wanneung.

