-Let go.
-Hey.

00:56:03.093 --> 00:56:04.173
Listen.

00:56:04.293 --> 00:56:05.853
Can you listen to me first?

00:56:11.333 --> 00:56:12.533
Don’t go.

00:56:13.773 --> 00:56:15.533
Please don’t go. I’m begging you.

00:56:21.773 --> 00:56:22.853
Please.

00:56:28.333 --> 00:56:30.773
Please give me some time.

00:56:45.493 --> 00:56:48.333
Are Win and Wanneung dating?

00:56:52.373 --> 00:56:53.933
Are you living in the same house?

00:56:53.933 --> 00:56:55.333
How long have you been living together?

00:56:55.333 --> 00:56:57.493
Will you hold a press conference,
or are you getting married?

00:56:57.533 --> 00:57:00.213
A rising superstar
and a comeback star are dating.

00:57:00.213 --> 00:57:01.493
This is going to be huge.

00:57:01.533 --> 00:57:02.893
-Yes, yes.
-Yes, yes.

00:57:02.933 --> 00:57:05.733
Are you really dating?
Please answer our questions.

00:57:05.773 --> 00:57:07.773
-Win, please answer.
-Are you dating Wanneung?

00:57:07.773 --> 00:57:08.893
What’s really going on?

00:57:08.893 --> 00:57:11.653
-Are you going to hold a press conference?
-Are you really dating Wanneung?

00:57:11.693 --> 00:57:13.613
-Win, where are you going?
-Wanneung!

00:57:13.653 --> 00:57:15.333
-Please listen first.
-Please answer.

00:57:15.333 --> 00:57:18.053
-Win Pawee, we want to know. Please tell us.
-Please answer.

00:57:18.053 --> 00:57:20.653
-Please answer.
-Are you going to hold a press conference?

00:57:20.653 --> 00:57:21.813
A press conference...

00:57:21.813 --> 00:57:23.333
Are you okay?

00:57:26.493 --> 00:57:28.693
How did the reporters know you were here?

00:57:28.853 --> 00:57:30.453
I didn’t tell anyone.

00:57:30.693 --> 00:57:32.573
What should we do?

00:57:34.733 --> 00:57:35.933
I think...

00:57:35.933 --> 00:57:37.813
someone must have followed us.

00:57:38.133 --> 00:57:39.333
Or...

00:57:41.053 --> 00:57:42.693
someone tipped off the reporters.

00:57:43.573 --> 00:57:45.173
Are you going to hold a press conference?

00:57:45.213 --> 00:57:46.453
This news is going to be huge.

00:57:46.493 --> 00:57:49.653
-Seriously, that’s Win.
-Yes, it is.

00:57:49.653 --> 00:57:52.133
Win, Wanneung, please come back
and answer a few questions.

00:57:52.173 --> 00:57:53.173
See you...

00:57:53.253 --> 00:57:54.613
Who would tell them?

00:57:55.013 --> 00:57:56.933
Only a few people know about this...

00:57:59.653 --> 00:58:01.053
P’Waanwaan.

00:58:03.813 --> 00:58:04.933
But I don't think it's her.

00:58:04.973 --> 00:58:06.333
I think it is.

00:58:07.533 --> 00:58:09.893
Then what should I do?

00:58:09.933 --> 00:58:12.293
Wanneung, you don't have to do anything.

00:58:12.293 --> 00:58:15.773
We'll just stay quiet and not respond.
The news will die down.

00:58:15.893 --> 00:58:17.413
For me, it's fine.

00:58:17.493 --> 00:58:19.813
Hardly anyone even knows me.

00:58:21.133 --> 00:58:23.173
I'm only worried about you.

00:58:23.733 --> 00:58:25.693
You're about to return to acting.

00:58:26.013 --> 00:58:28.013
If news like this comes out,

00:58:28.053 --> 00:58:29.453
it could damage your reputation

00:58:29.453 --> 00:58:31.173
and affect the film.

00:58:35.813 --> 00:58:37.613
I need to leave here as soon as possible.

00:58:37.653 --> 00:58:39.253
Then the problem will end.

00:58:41.173 --> 00:58:42.373
Wanneung.

00:58:43.773 --> 00:58:45.453
Even if you leave, it won't help.

00:58:45.453 --> 00:58:47.333
The reporters already know.

00:58:48.893 --> 00:58:50.693
Then what do you want to do?

00:58:57.213 --> 00:58:58.333
Like this.

00:58:59.253 --> 00:59:01.493
I only cause trouble for you.

00:59:02.853 --> 00:59:05.253
Please just let me move somewhere else.

00:59:35.893 --> 00:59:37.013
Meedee, you're here.

00:59:37.573 --> 00:59:39.653
Are you really living with Wanneung?

00:59:39.733 --> 00:59:41.253
That’s your bag, right?

00:59:41.253 --> 00:59:42.573
Take it and leave.

00:59:42.573 --> 00:59:44.093
Wanneung is staying here.

00:59:44.093 --> 00:59:45.493
We’re a couple.

01:00:07.846 --> 01:00:08.846
Win.

01:00:08.886 --> 01:00:09.886
Win.

01:00:10.606 --> 01:00:12.086
It's May.

01:00:12.686 --> 01:00:14.846
Win, please open the door.

01:00:17.086 --> 01:00:18.246
Win.

01:00:21.166 --> 01:00:22.646
Can you hear me?

01:00:22.886 --> 01:00:24.046
Win.

01:00:25.366 --> 01:00:26.406
Hey.

01:00:27.046 --> 01:00:29.126
Why are you yelling
in front of my friend's house?

01:00:29.166 --> 01:00:32.166
Didn't you see the news that
the two of them are living here together?

01:00:32.206 --> 01:00:33.726
I don't care about that news.

01:00:33.766 --> 01:00:35.686
If you don't care,
why did you come here?

01:00:36.046 --> 01:00:38.086
Wanneung was the one
who told me to come here.

01:00:38.646 --> 01:00:39.726
Win.

01:00:41.126 --> 01:00:42.526
Meedee, you're here.

01:00:43.446 --> 01:00:44.446
May.

01:00:44.686 --> 01:00:45.806
How did you get here?

01:00:48.006 --> 01:00:50.486
Are you really living with Wanneung?

01:00:50.966 --> 01:00:51.966
Wanneung.

01:00:52.366 --> 01:00:54.326
Why is this woman still here?

01:01:04.566 --> 01:01:06.046
Shameless.

01:01:06.246 --> 01:01:08.446
Living in someone else's house like this.

01:01:14.086 --> 01:01:15.246
Wanneung.

01:01:15.366 --> 01:01:17.446
What's wrong? Why didn't you tell me?

01:01:17.686 --> 01:01:19.166
If you don't have a place to stay,

01:01:19.326 --> 01:01:21.086
you can stay at my house.

01:01:21.326 --> 01:01:22.526
Fine.

01:01:22.606 --> 01:01:24.166
Then you two should move out together.

01:01:25.126 --> 01:01:26.726
That’s your bag, right?

01:01:26.846 --> 01:01:28.326
Take it and leave.

01:01:39.006 --> 01:01:40.726
Wanneung is staying here.

01:01:42.566 --> 01:01:44.246
Wanneung isn’t going anywhere.

01:01:45.086 --> 01:01:46.126
Win.

01:01:50.286 --> 01:01:52.326
And what right do you have to stop my girlfriend?

01:01:52.406 --> 01:01:54.486
Hey, watch what you're saying.

01:01:55.766 --> 01:01:57.606
Wanneung has told you many times

01:01:57.606 --> 01:01:59.006
that you can only be a friend.

01:02:03.846 --> 01:02:05.326
You know, right?

01:02:05.846 --> 01:02:07.406
When someone isn’t the one,

01:02:07.606 --> 01:02:10.086
no matter how hard you try, they’re not.

01:02:15.046 --> 01:02:16.966
So you got friend-zoned?

01:02:18.326 --> 01:02:19.966
Hey, you...

01:02:22.646 --> 01:02:23.766
Win.

01:02:24.646 --> 01:02:26.926
Why would you let her live here?

01:02:28.326 --> 01:02:30.486
Your reputation will be ruined.

01:02:31.086 --> 01:02:33.246
And we’re about to star in a film together.

01:02:34.486 --> 01:02:36.446
We’re supposed to be a shipping couple.

01:02:36.446 --> 01:02:38.646
And now we’re starting to gain fans.

01:02:38.886 --> 01:02:41.246
If fans find out about this,

01:02:41.326 --> 01:02:43.526
they’ll be very hurt.

01:02:51.246 --> 01:02:53.206
I’ll publicly apologize to the fans.

01:02:56.086 --> 01:02:57.446
I've already prepared myself.

01:03:00.046 --> 01:03:03.046
My reputation isn’t good anyway.

01:03:05.766 --> 01:03:08.286
If it gets ruined again, that’s fine.

01:03:12.126 --> 01:03:14.046
What do you mean?

01:04:47.046 --> 01:04:48.726
Wanneung and I

01:04:50.166 --> 01:04:51.486
are dating.

01:04:53.126 --> 01:04:54.926
We’re a couple.

01:04:57.526 --> 01:04:58.606
Win...

01:05:29.006 --> 01:05:32.686
Wanneung finally has a girlfriend
like everyone else.

01:05:32.726 --> 01:05:35.086
Excuse me, are you Wanneung?

01:05:35.086 --> 01:05:37.526
Your dream is about to come true now.

01:05:37.566 --> 01:05:39.566
You're going to become the star
you've always dreamed of.

01:05:39.566 --> 01:05:41.726
You're getting really famous now.

01:05:41.766 --> 01:05:43.126
Win.

01:05:43.886 --> 01:05:45.326
You're so beautiful, Win.

01:05:45.326 --> 01:05:47.646
Since you're already packing your things,

01:05:47.686 --> 01:05:49.726
you might as well move into this room with me.

01:05:49.726 --> 01:05:52.566
The whole internet is saying
you and Win live in the same house.

01:05:52.606 --> 01:05:54.406
I'd like to withdraw from this film.

01:05:54.446 --> 01:05:55.646
So everything will end.

01:05:55.926 --> 01:05:58.806
But I want Wanneung to continue
acting in this film.

01:05:59.046 --> 01:06:00.486
Belle, does my hair smell nice today?

01:06:01.566 --> 01:06:02.926
How many times did you wash it?

01:06:03.006 --> 01:06:04.926
Twelve times today.

01:06:05.846 --> 01:06:07.006
Her hair smells really nice.

01:06:07.046 --> 01:06:08.846
She washed it enough
to last until the end of the year.

01:06:09.686 --> 01:06:11.686
Yeah, yeah. Let them play first.
(Fussing by the pool)

01:06:11.686 --> 01:06:12.766
Check this background first.

01:06:12.806 --> 01:06:14.806
-Action.
-Okay, that’s enough.

01:06:16.926 --> 01:06:18.006
Wanneung, I’m here.

01:06:18.046 --> 01:06:19.926
-One last action left.
-No, no.

01:06:20.446 --> 01:06:22.006
(Personal heater)

01:06:22.046 --> 01:06:23.406
Next scene, no more water scenes.

01:06:23.446 --> 01:06:25.566
Wanneung is way too water-phobic.

01:06:25.566 --> 01:06:27.846
Now we’re about to become Belle-phobic.